{"tid":546842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個自覺深受屋企人影響既性格","createTime":"2018-02-01T01:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T08:46:33.000Z","uid":85474,"like":60,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"964725a516c03c11ae67138a7a9eb3c8ca973625","tid":546842,"uid":85474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"細個既時候唔多覺，但諗返轉頭發現屋企人對自己既性格影響幾深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然你可以話唔好咩都推比屋企人，<br />\n宜家大個發現有問題當然會慢慢去改，<br />\n但以前唔爲意就會有好大影響，而且可能個影響真係好無形<br />\n<br />\n抛個磚先<br />\n<br />\n我就細個同老豆閙交既時候，老豆每次就會掉我啲野<br />\n試過有次掉左我前後加埋用咗最少幾千蚊買既pokemon卡<br />\n開頭當然唔開心，但慢慢就覺得無咗就算<br />\n後來感覺我好似唔太會珍惜野，就算感情都係覺得無咗就算<br />\n我諗呢個係我老豆其中一個影響我最大既性格"},{"pid":"4cb5abf4c3ffd3bf74b91b8dec5d4dd3fafc7c94","tid":546842,"uid":7125,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"抑鬱<br />\n鬱到盡就燥狂<br />\n細個唔知點解 而家睇番我根本就係我老豆同老母既結合體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗乜柒都好撚灰<br />\n去到好大個先識控制情緒同人社交 不過間歇性個人就會好撚down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717220fe54d40a87f25d14ad4c0263c412a57267","tid":546842,"uid":51978,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:47:12.000Z","msg":"畀佢地日日人身攻擊 鬧我厚面皮 不知羞恥<br />\n結果面皮好薄 好顧忌人地對我嘅睇法"},{"pid":"54c1f85754301f2b6c1da6105a734bba9ecffe3b","tid":546842,"uid":85474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb5abf4c3ffd3bf74b91b8dec5d4dd3fafc7c94","tid":546842,"uid":7125,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"抑鬱<br />\n鬱到盡就燥狂<br />\n細個唔知點解 而家睇番我根本就係我老豆同老母既結合體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗乜柒都好撚灰<br />\n去到好大個先識控制情緒同人社交 不過間歇性個人就會好撚down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"巴打屋企人係都咪無咩社交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062ce79e5744a9cc5a1e4964da55db4966f58d85","tid":546842,"uid":45627,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"受我老豆影響我係有少少幽默<br />\n因為佢份人都幾鐘意搞笑<br />\n<br />\n但正正因為咁<br />\n佢從來對我都係有彈冇讚, 拎我嚟講笑<br />\n就算人地笑我佢都會覺得冇乜嘢, 甚至一齊講<br />\n所以我份人係好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee8b4698401465a1722489dd713d351ed233ae9","tid":546842,"uid":85474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54c1f85754301f2b6c1da6105a734bba9ecffe3b","tid":546842,"uid":85474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb5abf4c3ffd3bf74b91b8dec5d4dd3fafc7c94","tid":546842,"uid":7125,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"抑鬱<br />\n鬱到盡就燥狂<br />\n細個唔知點解 而家睇番我根本就係我老豆同老母既結合體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗乜柒都好撚灰<br />\n去到好大個先識控制情緒同人社交 不過間歇性個人就會好撚down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"巴打屋企人係都咪無咩社交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打屋企人係咪都係無咩社交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910893b9ef2ce70c118d6ca5280ca054d271243b","tid":546842,"uid":164863,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n個人好唔識拒絕人 同成日委屈都唔識出聲幫自己<br />\n好似我老母咁<br />\n可能由細到大都見佢都係咁<br />\n真係影響好深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人好內弱 真係完全跟足我老母"},{"pid":"7326ebb06e5840446bde14653e7862586e2d3db2","tid":546842,"uid":153279,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:13:59.000Z","msg":"有 老母好照顧身邊既人又好好人緣<br />\n所以大個左都不知不覺多左關心親既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66eee0e6a800f88ecd29ffbe0c5eaa1c34c0910","tid":546842,"uid":37922,"like":8,